# init(rawValue:)

**Initializer**

Creates an option with a string value.

## Declaration

```swift
init(rawValue: String)
```

## Parameters

- **rawValue**: A string value that represents a [doc://Vision/documentation/Vision/VNVideoProcessingOption/frameCadence] or [doc://Vision/documentation/Vision/VNVideoProcessingOption/timeInterval].
